<p><strong>Cost calculation (Medium):</strong> 1M records × 1,000 tokens = 1B tokens. Gemini Flash batch: (1B × $0.30/M × 0.5 discount) + (1B × $2.50/M × 0.5 discount) ≈ $150 + $1,250 = $1,400. Note: actual cost per record is ~$0.0014, or $0.14/100-record batch.</p>

